			<article class="main container col4">
								<header class="maincol">
										<h1 class="pagetitle">A Lighthouse Keeper Hangs Up Her Bonnet</h1>
										<h2 class="dek singlepagecontainer">Celebrating the experiences of Sally Snowman, who will soon retire as the only female lighthouse keeper in the Boston Light’s 307-year history.</h2>
										<section class="singlebyline singlepagecontainer">
						<h3 class="invis">Authored by</h3>
						by  
										<a href="https://hakaimagazine.com/profiles/diana-cervantes/" class="tagmanager" id="author_link_top" >Diana Cervantes</a>								<br/>
