																																															<a href="https://hakaimagazine.com/profiles/diana-cervantes/" class="tagmanager" id="author_link_bottom" >
											<div class="container col3 ">
												<div class="col span2"><p>Diana Cervantes is an independent visual journalist based in New York City and the southwestern United States. Focused on conservation, climate change, and interspecies relationships, Cervantes is dedicated to shedding light on individuals at the forefront of these pressing themes. Her long-form, visual storytelling approach not only captures the essence of these stories but also fosters meaningful relationships, trust, and a comprehensive understanding of the topics she explores.</p></div>
